datastructures.tables

Interface ITable<K,E>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - type of the key of elements stored in the table.
    E - type of elements stored in the table.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TablePair<K,E>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ISortableTable<K,E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinarySearchTree, NonsortedSeqenceTable, SortedSeqenceTable

    public interface ITable<K,E>
extends java.lang.Iterable<TablePair<K,E>>
    Interface for work with tables.
